info.name: Tumblr - Missing E Warning Remover
info.description: This script hides the Missing E warning whenever it tries to appear.
info.additionalInfo: Please note that I made this quick fix in a matter of seconds. The constant warning became unbearable. It works on my Chrome but I am not sure if it will work on every computer, every browser, etc. If you have problems, uninstall it. Hopefully this will be of use to some of you!
